                            "technique",
                            "T1566"
                        ]
                    ]
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "Akira operators may utilize phishing campaigns to gain initial access to victim environments by delivering malicious attachments, embedded links, or weaponized documents through email. These phishing emails are often crafted to appear legitimate and may impersonate trusted organizations, business partners, or internal personnel."
